ratings.question_text: What is your overall assessment of this course?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: Sure, it was a great seminar overall.
Great readings, but more input from the professor (an intro or a short lecture) would give more focus to each class.Overall, would recommend.

Yes, I would recommend this course to any student working on modernism. The only way to get a serious grasp on the diverse and varied 'production' of the Constructivists is through deep immersion...and even then, much of the material remains fairly obscure.
